{"tid":1233051,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"隔左3年，泛民同本土終於做到第一次既合作","createTime":"2019-06-16T17:18:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T02:00:23.000Z","uid":34355,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1042c5a369ea0e8ad35e784ce83056c1f6be9817","tid":1233051,"uid":34355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:18:37.000Z","msg":"自從6月9後，我開始loop返天琦以前既片，望睇返佢講過既野，做過既事，根本可以完全fit返入哩幾日既遊行同示威入面。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Q-kGIHSHLl0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQ-kGIHSHLl0&d=sdtaPhne9yHE0zuhYC4X4f5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=e483d63c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Q-kGIHSHLl0</a><br />\n睇下下面條片，當楊岳橋當選之後，天琦同楊大狀都認為本土同泛民可以共存，當然我唔認為香港仲有險可守。哩3年內經歷過無數次既割蓆，對鬧，到今年6月終於透過一群無名勇武義士同班後生泛民證明到真係可以共存，遊行時和平，凌晨時靜待，到適當衝既時候衝。可能仲有班和理非唔認同，但係事實證明左有時勇武抗爭係會令到當權者退步。<br />\n黎緊就係選舉，與其成日諗選舉點樣鎅本土/泛民票，不如諗下點樣配合打沉建制同哩個港共政權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=T1pcg3KI6fY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DT1pcg3KI6fY&d=sdtaPhne9yHE0zuhYC4X4f5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=de4ac892\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=T1pcg3KI6fY</a>"},{"pid":"7c39d44889dfb8d313c706bb96bff8c4d91b7ba9","tid":1233051,"uid":29080,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:21:07.000Z","msg":"已經冇本錢分裂"},{"pid":"0fb0c871dd6349e5bb6361a85c01e8f203cea12f","tid":1233051,"uid":34355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c39d44889dfb8d313c706bb96bff8c4d91b7ba9","tid":1233051,"uid":29080,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:21:07.000Z","msg":"已經冇本錢分裂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:28:56.000Z","msg":"無錯，打咁多野都係想支持泛民既各位諗一下係咪真係有險可守。<br />\n我當時間回到6月9日夜晚，當柒婆發聲明繼續硬推條例漠視103萬人和平遊行既時候各位係咪仲覺得哩個政權仲信得過。<br />\n今日上街見到好多人講到612唔係暴動，我想各位當日認為魚革係暴動既人反思一下: 當日係咪真係暴動?泛民同本土係咪真係要係對立?"},{"pid":"78cea845023bd4654b7795d9a2d551b2d93eefe6","tid":1233051,"uid":83060,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:29:52.000Z","msg":"各有各做同合作爭好遠"},{"pid":"1700b2880f6688b1775e5a61866d406546bdb43b","tid":1233051,"uid":144883,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:33:09.000Z","msg":"各有各做已經好好，<br />\n請child登仔停止「捉鬼」歪風<br />\n不要再走舊路，thz"},{"pid":"90bfe5922cef8f8e31bb1715843594562118b773","tid":1233051,"uid":29080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"78cea845023bd4654b7795d9a2d551b2d93eefe6","tid":1233051,"uid":83060,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:29:52.000Z","msg":"各有各做同合作爭好遠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:33:38.000Z","msg":"就算唔合作都唔好鬼打鬼<br />\n到時保蝗狗又漁人得利"},{"pid":"ecfaf0d4936d22ffee917bdae2a8335621b618bf","tid":1233051,"uid":38461,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:34:07.000Z","msg":"佢suggested video有呢段<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=36olyar0wHE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D36olyar0wHE&d=sdtaPhne9yHE0zuhYC4X4f5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=7f6bb915\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=36olyar0wHE</a><br />\n好想快啲天琦出返嚟...."},{"pid":"63c3e7351822816947260858cd1f20b3c1188bfe","tid":1233051,"uid":146340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:36:19.000Z","msg":"本土死咗啦 邊有合作"},{"pid":"62be98675f109f74cf534e7768f50bb0d9916be8","tid":1233051,"uid":34355,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"78cea845023bd4654b7795d9a2d551b2d93eefe6","tid":1233051,"uid":83060,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:29:52.000Z","msg":"各有各做同合作爭好遠"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:37:02.000Z","msg":"至少起碼大家會有一個妥協<br />\n發夢夢到612下晝唔係泛民勇武屌黎屌去，即使衝既時候，同意既一齊衝唔同意既就退後，完全無狗咬狗情況。"},{"pid":"675903c50460f56424ac9ced104f347e05e77f4e","tid":1233051,"uid":131125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62be98675f109f